{"tid":2265143,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"致Cathie Wood的一封信: 昨日, 我菲律賓工人行過街市...","createTime":"2020-10-31T07:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T09:22:26.000Z","uid":347193,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5ed94f2bf66d64020945329012238ff070c54f","tid":2265143,"uid":347193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:53:45.000Z","msg":"昨日，我菲律賓工人行過街市，<br />\n聽到有個連登仔講話有條友仔叫女股神，係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈哈&hellip;&hellip;我當堂嚇左一跳，然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個世界，居然有人自稱女股神，咁即係分明當佢流jeh！<br />\n拿！佢就叫燈神，你炒股都要靠隻tesla啦，佢就睬你都o徒氣，<br />\n直情睇穿個市o既，呢d就叫特異功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度有隻股叫跌塔，只要佢輕輕一吹，就即刻變為一隻殘左o既屎塔<br />\n咩呀，因為佢未發功丫嘛。佢發左功呀，跌撚到停埋牌都得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話佢果然無厘頭呀，佢夠話你未訓醒戇九九咯。<br />\n望咩呀﹖條氣唔順呀﹖發個輪黎大家研究下。<br />\n當然，你要補番一千幾百萬過我就唔在講架啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啤咩呀﹖學野唔使錢呀﹖抄底佢聯絡電話係香港︰3345678，<br />\n我再重覆一次係香港︰3345678。<br />\n<br />\n你唔搵佢，我冇所謂，因為呢d絕對係你o既損失。<br />\n星期五十點後鐘唔好打黎，<br />\n因為佢仲要番工！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489d31eadd88c4590a2223bd9dafa5ea9d73a6c0","tid":2265143,"uid":4050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有點尷尬"},{"pid":"52e6ece798e8b46ab2d7efbbca740f846c721c43","tid":2265143,"uid":120908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"豬到傻左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddae46d74485fe9bf2069bccb4cef15eb9275c3","tid":2265143,"uid":347193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kR6Xo3K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkR6Xo3K.png&h=f8de58ec&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}